### ============================================================
### 4) 채팅방 확인
### ============================================================
### 행사 생성 후 chat-service가 자동으로 채팅방을 만든다.
### 아래는 eventId로 채팅방이 생성됐는지 확인하는 용도다.

GET {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/rooms/event?eventId={{eventId1}}
GET {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/rooms/event?eventId={{eventId2}}
GET {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/rooms/event?eventId={{eventId3}}

### ============================================================
### 4-1) 채팅방 강제 오픈
### ============================================================
### 조회 결과로 받은 chatRoomId를 넣으면 강제로 OPEN 상태로 바꾼다.
### 필요하면 response script로 client.global.set("chatRoomId1", ...) 해서 저장한다.

PATCH {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/admin/rooms/{{chatRoomId1}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: {{adminUserRole}}

{
  "action": "FORCE_OPEN"
}

###
PATCH {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/admin/rooms/{{chatRoomId2}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: {{adminUserRole}}

{
  "action": "FORCE_OPEN"
}

###
PATCH {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/admin/rooms/{{chatRoomId3}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: {{adminUserRole}}

{
  "action": "FORCE_OPEN"
}

### ============================================================
### 메모
### IntelliJ HTTP Client에서는 각 응답의 data.id / data.eventId 등을
### response script로 client.global.set(...) 해서 저장할 수 있다.
### 예:
###   client.global.set("festivalCategoryId", response.body.data.id);
###   client.global.set("eventId1", response.body.data.id);
###   client.global.set("chatRoomId1", response.body.data.chatRoomId);
### 채팅방 ID도 eventId로 조회해서 따로 저장해두면 k6에서 재사용하기 편하다.

### Chat Message Seed Samples
### 수동 확인용 예시
### - 채팅방이 OPEN 상태여야 메시지 생성이 성공한다.


@chatUrl = http://localhost:8088
@adminUserId = 3e9605c7-3d25-4171-9c00-e83a10cccf25
@adminRole = ADMIN
@userId1 = b6137489-2e8a-4166-87aa-7651f61c219c
@userId2 = 4ee050e8-44e6-4764-8860-691322e23e59
@chatRoomId1=15a5f54f-6f52-4826-9bb7-0a226909cf58
@chatRoomId2=37ff80ae-7a2f-49cb-9e6c-9a16b221dc7c
@chatRoomId3=2383b1f1-317f-4dfd-85a5-531782c4228c


### 채팅방 조회
GET {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/rooms/event?eventId={{eventId}}

### 채팅방 강제 오픈
PATCH {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/admin/rooms/{{chatRoomId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{adminUserId}}
X-User-Role: {{adminRole}}

{
  "action": "FORCE_OPEN"
}

### 메시지 1
POST {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/rooms/{{chatRoomId1}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId1}}
X-User-Role: USER

{
  "content": "시드메시지 1"
}

### 메시지 2
POST {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/rooms/{{chatRoomId2}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId2}}
X-User-Role: USER

{
  "content": "시드메시지 2"
}

### 메시지 2
POST {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/rooms/{{chatRoomId3}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: {{userId2}}
X-User-Role: USER

{
  "content": "시드메시지 3"
}

### 메시지 목록 확인
GET {{chatUrl}}/v1/chat/rooms/{{chatRoomId3}}/messages?page=0&size=20
